{%- comment -%}
  SwopCase – Bundle context line (one sentence)
  ------------------------------------------------------------
  A short, honest context line that sits ABOVE the discount
  app widget on the PDP (between price and "In den Warenkorb").

  It only EXPLAINS the benefit in words. The actual discount
  logic stays with the Smart Automatic Discounts app, which is
  the single source of truth. This snippet never calculates or
  duplicates any discount.

  Phase 1: file is created only. It is NOT wired into any Dawn
  file yet (that happens in a later, approved phase).

  Styles live in assets/swopcase-theme.css (.swopcase-bundle-kontext).

  Optional param:
    {% render 'swopcase-bundle-kontext',
        text: 'Mehr Designs, mehr Vorteil: …' %}
{%- endcomment -%}

{{ 'swopcase-theme.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

{%- liquid
  assign kontext = text | default: 'Je mehr Swops, desto besser der Preis – dein <strong>Mengenrabatt</strong> wird automatisch im Warenkorb abgezogen.'
-%}

<div class="swopcase-bundle-kontext" role="note">
  <svg class="swopcase-bundle-kontext__icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
    <path d="M12 2l2.6 5.27L20.4 8l-4.2 4.1 1 5.8L12 15.1 6.8 17.9l1-5.8L3.6 8l5.8-.73z" />
  </svg>
  <p class="swopcase-bundle-kontext__text">{{ kontext }}</p>
</div>
